        <message_html><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Greetings</span><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">&nbsp;${employee_name},&nbsp;<br /></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: red;">Note this is an automated communication being sent by Clayton State University Human Resources</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">. <strong>For specific information concerning your Department, please contact your Hiring Manager. </strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">Congratulations on joining the Clayton State University Community!&nbsp; Please read this email carefully, there is a lot of information within and items that may require your action. </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Your Start Date</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">: </span><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">Please contact your Hiring Manager for specific information</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Your Department</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">: <span style="color: #000000;">${employee_name.department}</span><br /> </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Your Hiring Manager/Reports to Manager</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">: ${hiring_manager} /&nbsp; ${reports_to_manager}<br /><br /></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Your New Hire Orientation Date</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">: ${new_hire_orientation_date}<br />&nbsp; </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Your Employee Credentials, if applicable</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">: Please contact your Hiring Manager for this information. Once you obtain this information you can activate your credentials <a title="here" href="https://account.clayton.edu/activate/identify" target="_blank">here</a>. Activating your credentials will allow access to your Clayton.edu email, your network access. </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Multi-Factor Authentication</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">: CSU uses multi-factor authentication which <span style="color: #222222;">is a method of confirming your identity. Please activate your MFA <a title="here" href="https://auth.clayton.edu/login?service=https://apps.clayton.edu/directory/casHandler" target="_blank">here</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">OneUSG Connect</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">: Clayton State University utilizes OneUSG Connect which is our web based Employee Self Service (ESS) system.&nbsp; You will have access to OneUSG Connect through the Single Sign-On Self Service URL to submit time, complete absence requests, view documents, update information, etc. by clicking <a title="here" href="https://oneusgconnect.usg.edu/" target="_blank">here</a>.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Required Training</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">: Also you will need to take and complete <strong>ALL</strong> necessary required trainings within 3-5 days of employment. More information can be accessed <a title="here" href="http://www.clayton.edu/human-resources/New-Hire-Orientation" target="_blank">here</a>.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;"><strong style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14.6667px;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Employee Handbooks</span></strong>: Click <a title="here" href="http://www.clayton.edu/human-resources/Handbooks" target="_blank">here</a> to access all employee handbooks.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;"><strong style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14.6667px;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;">Centralized Payroll Schedule</span></strong>: Click <a title="here" href="http://www.clayton.edu/payroll/Payroll-Schedule" target="_blank">here</a> to access the payroll calendar.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">Again, welcome to Clayton State University. Please feel free to contact your Hiring Manager/Reports to Manager or HR with any questions. </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">Thank you,&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">Human Resources</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">o: 678.466.4230 | f: 678.466.4239 </span></p>]]></message_html>
